I only managed to find this feeling

114
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,780
when I was playing extreme sports.

115
00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,140
So I think

116
00:05:26,140 --> 00:05:27,460
this is my true passion.

117
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:29,700
I found the direction of my life.

118
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:35,540
You want to

119
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:37,140
to be a firefighter?

120
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:41,780
With Deputy Director Yu's sacrifice

121
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:43,780
and Nan Chu going to America,

122
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:47,140
I am more than determined about this.

123
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:49,900
I think we should pursue

124
00:05:50,700 --> 00:05:52,380
