125
00:05:53,220 --> 00:05:54,340
That's what makes life worthwhile.

126
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,140
Same goes for you.

127
00:05:58,260 --> 00:05:59,260
Since you like art so much,

128
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:00,020
