158
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:21,700
what was your purpose

159
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:23,460
when you established Fude Group back then?

160
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:27,100
Why do you suddenly ask?

161
00:08:28,940 --> 00:08:30,700
Back then, my thought was very simple.

162
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:32,620
It was to allow our family

163
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:34,220
to live a good life,

164
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:36,220
and when I get old,

165
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:38,060
I get to enjoy myself.

166
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:40,100
Hasn't it already come true?

167
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:42,180
Why are you still working so hard?

168
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,730
Actually,

169
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,700
it's easy to build up the empire,

170
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:50,580
but it's difficult to protect it.

171
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:53,580
Think about it. There are so many people in the company

172
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:55,700
who are relying on us for survival.

173
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:57,220
How can I quit?

174
00:08:58,420 --> 00:08:59,300
And you!

175
00:08:59,970 --> 00:09:01,220
You always make me worry.

176
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:03,460
If you are doing this for me,

177
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:04,220
then please do not worry.

178
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:10,580
You were right before.

179
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,220
I couldn't find a direction in life.

180
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:15,580
I always did whatever I want.

181
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,460
But I found it now.

182
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:19,700
And it's even thanks to you.

183
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:22,580
If you didn't make me

184
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:23,820
do the show, Flaming Youth,

185
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:26,300
maybe I would have stayed confused even up till now.

186
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:30,820
What's this direction that you have found?

187
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:35,220
I applied to be a firefighter.

188
00:09:39,180 --> 00:09:39,700
Why?

189
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:44,700
I have always wanted to do something

190
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:45,980
to prove myself to you.

191
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:49,970
But I never thought why was there a need for me to prove myself.

192
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:52,490
So what

193
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:53,340
if I got recognition from you?

194
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:58,100
There are so many people in this world.

195
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,300
If I prove to them one by one,

196
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,100
just how tired will I be?

197
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:05,580
Actually, the only thing I have to face

198
00:10:06,570 --> 00:10:07,410
is myself.

199
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:09,580
I had to ask myself honestly.

200
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:11,740
What I want is a sense of accomplishment

201
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:12,740
and presence.

202
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:14,420
And these two feelings

203
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:16,300
can be found on firefighters.

204
00:10:18,220 --> 00:10:18,580
Being a firefighter

205
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:20,340
is the value of life that I have been seeking.

206
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:25,690
Fine.

207
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:28,700
If you think so,

208
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:30,580
it means you've grown up.

209
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:33,860
I support you.

210
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,060
What about you, Dad?

211
00:10:42,340 --> 00:10:42,820
I...

212
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:45,940
Look.

213
00:10:47,330 --> 00:10:48,580
