215
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:53,860
Also, our family is doing well now.

216
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,700
It's time to enjoy life.

217
00:10:58,740 --> 00:10:59,730
Enjoy life?

218
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:01,820
What about the company?

219
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:03,740
Leave it to a professional management team.

220
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:05,820
Times are moving so fast these days.

221
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,980
It's no longer the time to be fighting all by yourself.

222
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:10,580
Think about how old you are now.

223
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:12,580
No matter how hard you work,

224
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:13,460
