225
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:18,580
Dad.

226
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,980
Actually, work is not the only thing in life.

227
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:25,300
You've already done up to 90 points.

228
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:27,500
Save ten points for yourself.

229
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,220
Take my mom out

230
00:11:29,940 --> 00:11:30,820
