233
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:45,700
That's enough.

234
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:46,420
Let's go home.

235
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:49,100
I have to finish my work.

236
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:50,340
Please listen to me for once.

237
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:52,460
You want to kidnap me?

238
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:53,500
Yes, I want to kidnap you.

239
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:54,100
You...

240
