How is it?

243
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:09,690
It looks good.

244
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:10,940
Of course.

245
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:16,860
Not bad.

246
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:17,980
It's fresh.

247
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:18,930
Let me tell you.

248
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,460
