253
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,100
Let me tell you.

254
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:31,300
I can cook a wide variety of dishes.

255
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:38,860
Hey,

256
00:12:38,860 --> 00:12:40,220
