268
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:05,100
When Nan Chu comes back,

269
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:05,820
let's continue to work with her.

270
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:06,460
Okay.

271
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:10,460
Let's wish Nan Chu all the best.

272
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:12,820
Wait.

273
00:13:12,820 --> 00:13:14,100
And also Coach Lin.

274
00:13:15,450 --> 00:13:16,060
Right.

275
00:13:16,340 --> 00:13:19,100
Let's wish all of us good luck then.

276
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:20,180
May we all get better.

277
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:20,460
Okay.

